==Notes==
{{notelist |notes=
{{efn |name=year |1=
Contemporary newspaper records show that the most or all of the Fairy Tales collections were published the fall for the Christmas gift-book season, in both Britain and America. Some are generally catalogued as publications of the following year, from their title pages.
